name: Goerli ETH
public_notice: "Goerli Testnet" is an one of Ethereum Chain's many testnet that serves as a test environment for Ethereum developers, and is facing deprecation. It should also be noted that these testnet tokens can be obtained for free as it is meant for testing of Ethereum smart contract in a sandbox environment.
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.
